<H3><A NAME="News10"><FONT  COLOR=#800000>NEWS RELEASE			
July 23, 1997</FONT></A></H3>
<P>
<B>FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE<BR>Wednesday, July 23, 1997</P>
<P>
Lajuanda J. Holder<BR>
Director of Investor Relations<BR>
(915)688-3419<BR>
<A HREF="mailto:cwei@worldnet.att.net">email - cwei@worldnet.att.net</A></P>
